  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><p><b>William</b> is a given name in Westeros and may refer to:\n</p>\n<ul><li><a href=\"/index.php/William_Mooton\" title=\"William Mooton\">William Mooton</a>, Lord of Maidenpool</li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/William_Tortoll\" title=\"William Tortoll\">William Tortoll</a>, a knight</li>\n<li>Lord William Baratheon and his son of the same name, characters mentioned in <a href=\"/index.php/Lineages_and_Histories_book_(HBO_Game_of_Thrones)#House_Baratheon\" title=\"Lineages and Histories book (HBO Game of Thrones)\">Season 1</a> of <i>Game of Thrones</i></li>\n<li>William Flowers, a First Builder of the Night's Watch mentioned in <a href=\"/index.php/List_of_characters_created_for_Game_of_Thrones#Episode_2:_The_House_of_Black_and_White\" title=\"List of characters created for Game of Thrones\">Season 5</a> of <i>Game of Thrones</i></li>\n<li>William, a Lannister man-at-arms mentioned in <a href=\"/index.php/List_of_characters_created_for_Game_of_Thrones#Episode_1:_Winterfell\" title=\"List of characters created for Game of Thrones\">Season 8</a> of <i>Game of Thrones</i></li></ul>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"See_also\">See also</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=William&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: See also\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li><a href=\"/index.php/Willam_(disambiguation)\" title=\"Willam (disambiguation)\">Willam (disambiguation)</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Willum_(disambiguation)\" title=\"Willum (disambiguation)\">Willum (disambiguation)</a></li></ul>\n\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nCached time: 20260403091621\nCache expiry: 1209600\nDynamic content: false\nCPU time usage: 0.003 seconds\nReal time usage: 0.004 seconds\nPreprocessor visited node count: 3/1000000\nPreproces